		<h1><a href="#main-idea">Our main idea</a></h1>
		<p>
			App that allows disabled person to send out requests to volunteers and other people, who are willing to help.
			Helpific platform aims to make daily activities easier for its users.
		</p>

		<h2><a href="#how">How ?</a></h2>
		<p>
			By putting together the individuals who need a favor and the ones who can do a favor.
			Helpific - it´s never been easier to give and get help. Helpific helps to connect those who need help with those who want to give help.
		</p>

		<h2><a href="#target-group">Our target group</a></h2>
		<p>
			Our target audience are 130 000 people with special needs in Estonia.
		</p>

		<h2><a href="#vision">Vision</a></h2>
		<p>
			We are starting local, but our idea is to go global with Helpific. We are non-profit organization, aiming to grow global, reaching every person with the need of help.
		</p>

